description: Taco Green-Go is a local, Chef owned and operated, eco-friendly, food truck, offering a rotating selection of fusion style street food. Some of their featured items are Mexican-style ceviche, fried macaroni and cheese balls and chicken mole tacos. Everything Taco Green-Go serves is fresh and homemade, no microwaves, canned, or pre-packaged food are used to produce meals.
name: Taco Green-Go!
